    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "This client has 2 workspace folders configured, but only shows the root directory. We should also show all workspace folders if there are any (or perhaps if there are >1)?\r\n\r\n```\r\nvim.lsp: Active Clients ~\r\n- gopls (id: 1)\r\n    Root directory: ~/src/some/project\r\n    Command: gopls\r\n    Settings: {\r\n      gopls = {\r\n        analyses = {\r\n          nilness = true,\r\n          unusedparams = true,\r\n          unusedwrite = true\r\n        }\r\n      }\r\n    }\r\n    Attached buffers: 1\r\n```\r\n\r\ncc @mfussenegger ",
    "closed_at": null,
    "closed_by": null,
